{"tid":569370,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"恒管招生預萬人報讀　校長料明年升格大學","createTime":"2018-02-22T15:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T16:10:56.000Z","uid":139077,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c3612c31655d72dc1b5f2d8de12159b53f834183","tid":569370,"uid":139077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"政府早前宣布為就讀自資課程的學生提供3萬港元學券資助，提供自資學士學位課程的院校，成為不少學生的出路。 <br />\n<br />\n恒生管理學院校長何順文表示，招生期內，包括今日(12日)即場報名及透過電子報名的學生，預期接近10,000人，比想像中熱烈，不少學生因3萬港元資助而提早到學院報名，預計提供1250個學額。當中管理學、企業管治、亞洲研究，三大課程最受歡迎，預期很快會額滿，又指有不少學生獲取5科25分的成績，或有八大院校取錄，仍選擇報讀恒管。 <br />\n<br />\n何順文形容，政府投放在自資課程的資助是給自資學院「打咗一支針」，又等同承認自資院校的地位。何指，不同意坊間指自資院校認受程度低，自資院校具靈活性及有助紓緩市場學位不足的問題，課程亦經學術及職業資歷評審局審批，較一般海外大學的課程嚴謹。 <br />\n<br />\n何續指，為滿足學生和家長對大學的要求，恒管亦正爭取升格為大學，預期明年有望「正名」。<br />\n<br />\n恒管邁向綜合大學之路 - 2014年7月14日<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20140714/00298_004.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20140714%2F00298_004.html&d=nbInO7Y79mucol7PE8CahwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=77d73312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20140714/00298_004.html</a><br />\n<br />\n恒管擬後年申升格大學 - 2015年9月15日<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20150915/00176_007.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20150915%2F00176_007.html&d=nbInO7Y79mucol7PE8CahwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=473eed44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20150915/00176_007.html</a><br />\n<br />\n恒管明年申升格大學 - 2016年2月20日<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160220/00176_073.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160220%2F00176_073.html&d=nbInO7Y79mucol7PE8CahwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7c3d0ff9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160220/00176_073.html</a><br />\n<br />\n恒管招生預萬人報讀　校長料明年升格大學 - 2017年7月12日<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170712/bkn-20170712170040620-0712_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170712%2Fbkn-20170712170040620-0712_00822_001.html&d=nbInO7Y79mucol7PE8CahwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e6dcfa17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170712/bkn-20170712170040620-0712_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c180b5451aca4b10b0c395bee32a6de889d8e2bf","tid":569370,"uid":139077,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"屌，間咁嘅野雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b04fbc9392675ecc1740c951e6426d2734a138","tid":569370,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"仆街，今次真係goal for U<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e5ce08e3e007b74418c2781212fdb75acc9d72","tid":569370,"uid":61257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"十幾年前中五畢業果陣<br />\n<br />\n哩間野好勁 而家點解攪成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a23b858d82014e29cdda65b610f4d0fcb8559d1","tid":569370,"uid":60665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2160867c3408b2460138e6665596d3c6a95dbfc4","tid":569370,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6e5ce08e3e007b74418c2781212fdb75acc9d72","tid":569370,"uid":61257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"十幾年前中五畢業果陣<br />\n<br />\n哩間野好勁 而家點解攪成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"果陣時係Al工廠， <br />\n一轉DSE就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"